"t m320 x90 he y1d0d ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Her work was more like the work of Sam-</div><div class="t m6a8 x90 he y1a07 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">uel, who was a teacher in Israel. </div><div class="t m862 x165 h1c y1a07 ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">But as </div><div class="t m56d x90 he y1ba3 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the Israel of old &quot;from Dan to Beersheba&quot; </div><div class="t m6c0 x90 he yf62 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">recognized in Samuel the work of a true </div><div class="t m57a x90 he y14cf ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">prophet of God, so have Seventh-day Ad-</div><div class="t m100 x90 he y18d6 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ventists recognized in the work of Ellen G. </div><div class="t md3 x90 he y1b3e ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">White an instrumentality of God&apos;s Holy </div><div class="t ma95 x90 he y180c ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Spirit sent to give direction and spiritual </div><div class="t mec2 x45 he y1b81 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">aid and comfort to His people. </div><div class="t m3e36 x5c h36 y2238 ff2 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">[35] </div><div class="t mecb x8f h36 y2238 ff2 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"> </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
